1. using
    the declaration of using should not be included in header files.
    the content of header files will be copyed to all files that contain it.
    this will conflict with some names defined.
    
2. string
    define in std
    #include<string>
    using std::string
    2.1 copy initialization and direct initialization
        std::cin>>string  from non-space to the last non-space
        getline(std::cin,string)    get all line until \n. \n will be included to cin, but will be discarded when assign to string.
        
        
        
        
        
